Package: trustpilotR
Type: Package
Title: Scrapes Reviews And Ratings From Trustpilot
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Peer Christensen
Maintainer: Peer Christensen <hr.pchristensen@gmail.com>
Description: This package scrapes user reviews of businesses from Trustpilot.
    It also gathers the ID of the reviewer, date of review and the star rating (1-5).
    You can set page_lim to control how many pages to parse.
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
Imports:
    rvest, 
    tidyverse,
    lubridate,
    stringr,
    dplyr,
    magrittr,
    purrr,
    jsonlite
URL: https://github.com/PeerChristensen/trustpilotR
BugReports: https://github.com/PeerChristensen/trustpilotR/issues
